raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "STIR" %}
{% set version = "5.0.0" %}
{% set sha256 = "f63f52266532bdc01d5e4749b724c8ae97cee03dde9450cb2ac5b75eedff1dce" %}
{% set treehash = "rel_5.0.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ treehash }}.tar.gz
  url: https://github.com/UCL/{{ name }}/archive/{{ treehash }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  skip: true  # [win and py<36]
  skip: true  # [win and vc<14]
  number: 2

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}
    - cmake
    - ninja
  host:
    - python
    - boost-cpp
    - numpy
    - swig
    - libitk-devel
    - libitk <5.2
    - nlohmann_json
    - openmp  # [osx]
    - libgomp  # [linux]
  run:
    - python
    - {{ pin_compatible('numpy') }}
    - {{ pin_compatible('libitk', min_pin='x.x', max_pin='x.x') }}
    - openmp  # [osx]
    - libgomp  # [linux]

test:
  requires:
    - pytest
  imports:
    - stir
  source_files:
    - recon_test_pack
    - examples
    - src/swig/test/python
  commands:
    - stir_config --config-dir
    - cd recon_test_pack
    - ./run_test_simulate_and_recon.sh  # [not win]
    - ./run_test_listmode_recon.sh  # [not win]
    - ./run_test_simulate_and_recon_with_motion.sh  # [not win]
    - ./run_scatter_tests.sh  # [not win]
    - ./run_tests.sh --nointbp  # [not win]
    - ./run_test_zoom_image.sh  # [not win]
    - run_tests  # [win]
    - cd SPECT
    - ./run_SPECT_tests.sh  # [not win]
    - cd ..
    - cd ..
    - pytest src/swig/test/python
